><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">- Voltagem: Bivolt</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">Dimensões:</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">- Altura: 120 mm</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">- Comprimento: 74 mm</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">- Largura: 37 mm</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">Corrente Máxima suportada pelo produto (AC): 16A</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">- 1 Saída - Máx 5A x 1</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">Recursos:</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">- Design moderno e elegante com esferas de LED embutidas</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">- Fácil instalação</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">- Compatibilidade universal: opera com qualquer tipo de lâmpada</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">- Acenda ou apague as luzes remotamente</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">- Acionamento inteligente: programe o agendamento para acender ou apagar as luzes e torne se